{"tid":6724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兩年前仲係中學雞既時候，見到前面位個女同學用官方app上高登......","createTime":"2016-11-27T13:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T14:17:18.000Z","uid":20899,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fdc71db675b20643d99af42f65aedd9d831c2e59","tid":6724,"uid":20899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:37:58.000Z","msg":"兩年前仲係中六雞，某日上上下堂發現前面位個女同學用緊官方個柒app上高登，<br />\n望住佢個背影都鄧佢可憐，就好似一個生係地獄鬼國既少女，根本唔知道出面既自由世界係幾咁美好...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是我拍拍佢膊頭，佢擰轉身，用疑惑既眼神望住我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同佢講：邊有人會用官方個垃圾app上高登架，你唔覺得又慢介面又柒既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只見佢一面愕然，細細聲咁講：吓......唔用呢個app可以點上高登呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢一刻，我只係想將佢拯救，逃離官方app呢個荒謬。<br />\n我一手拎左佢部iphone5s，上app store捉住佢手指解左個touchid，然後幫佢down左hkg +<br />\n再順手幫佢del埋個官方app，比返佢之後就繼續靜靜地上堂...<br />\n兩日後上返呢科既堂，佢突然擰轉身同我講：多謝你介紹個咁好用既app比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 遲下請你食餐飯報答你...<br />\n然後果個weekend就約左出黎食飯...仲直落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後既發展就唔多講<br />\n<br />\n兩年後，當hkg +正式宣布摺埋既時候，突然收到來自呢位女同學既snapchat...<br />\n佢話：仲記得當時你教我用hkg +上高登，而家冇得用了，好唔捨得嗚嗚...<br />\n當時lihkg仲未開，我只好同佢講：咁咪唔好上高登囉，唔駛死既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如今lihkg開左了，如果你見到呢個post，我想同你講：<br />\n可唔可以再同我食餐飯...？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  [black]再直落互射二十次[/black]"},{"pid":"e062aefdc868bfda5968c1a78ba7fd6463a6a85f","tid":6724,"uid":5848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:40:01.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"1dc8b04b905898b586c1e369e65e7b4b0f48e737","tid":6724,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a24a9e7145604a17168fbba1aaa70e698a805bb","tid":6724,"uid":23327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:45:13.000Z","msg":"巴打一定好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8676f6574642ac6327dd3a86b6ad4592fcacdc4","tid":6724,"uid":1878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:48:26.000Z","msg":"完來係你，請你食鮑魚好冇"},{"pid":"9fb14ba281122dfce73bada4cae86677a591b5bd","tid":6724,"uid":30674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"零分重作"},{"pid":"e13df12eb1b8e80580b120a18ef64c4803cc1fca","tid":6724,"uid":20899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:06:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打一定好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪有興趣食餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8235d4b9fbdfee1fe6afa9232efd496be018ac2c","tid":6724,"uid":6076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"唔搞gay，不了"}]}